name: Available
definition: The quality of being obtainable or accessible and ready for use or service.

name: Not Available
definition: The desired information is not available.

name: Biospecimen Retained and/or Contains DNA Indicator
definition: An indication as to whether biospecimens have been retained and/or whether those retained biospecimens contain DNA.

name: Biospecimens Not Retained
definition: An indication that no biospecimen samples were retained as reserve samples
parent: Biospecimen Retained and/or Contains DNA Indicator

name: Retained Specimens Contain DNA
definition: An indication that the retained biospecimens contain DNA.
parent: Biospecimen Retained and/or Contains DNA Indicator

name: Retained Specimens Do Not Contain DNA
definition: An indication that the retained biospecimens do not contain DNA.
parent: Biospecimen Retained and/or Contains DNA Indicator

name: Do Not Process
definition: An indication that a biospecimen should not be subjected to any treatment.
